    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/e1bca1f0e79d4c7bc34205f553ba6e88.poster.avif?t=1772208513\" width=800 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/e1bca1f0e79d4c7bc34205f553ba6e88.webm?t=1772208513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/e1bca1f0e79d4c7bc34205f553ba6e88.mp4?t=1772208513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/fc42655d4e159957380bc4a5e9025c34.poster.avif?t=1772208513\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/fc42655d4e159957380bc4a5e9025c34.webm?t=1772208513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/fc42655d4e159957380bc4a5e9025c34.mp4?t=1772208513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>   Battle of Arachnidia Demo</strong> is an addictive top-down arcade shooter, a modern interpretation of classic arcade games. The game is set in a battle mech battles with hordes of spider-robot warriors. Your task is to defend your base by exterminating all enemies, making your way through all sorts of tactical solutions, improving your robot and using various power-ups to help in the fight. The demo includes five levels of the game that will allow you to really get a feel for the gameplay and mechanics of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/3cc1e19cc41e72fbcf2f8b0aa100d943.avif?t=1772208513\" width=620 height=161 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > a lot of different levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > different levels with unique abilities of the enemy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > a system of easily obtaining bonuses that help repel attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > the level raising system of the individual fighting robot makes it more destructive</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244510/extras/e3562d78161448330353ae5b8ea10831.avif?t=1772208513\" width=620 height=161 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was completely developed by one person - Volodymyr Krysenko, as a tribute to classic arcade games.</p>",
